aces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"your observation is damn right. <br />\n我估你講既financial risk management 係指market risk, liquidity risk and traded credit risk<br />\n係依個scope 入面, 係有分risk management and risk control.<br />\nfor risk management, 大家都prefer 有經驗人士, 所以trader assistant,  experienced trader都係target candidate 之一. 主要原因係佢地就係market risk 既最前線, counterparties 就係global markets trader.<br />\n當然都有D人係做做下risk control 轉.. 但依D就講network more than knowledge. <br />\n咁fresh grad就多數都係做reporting, 做risk control. 但越黎越多由offshore team 去做..所以入行先好似越黎越難啦..<br />\n<br />\n大概就係咁."},{"pid":"a782786d2c052711ab4f383963ff6e334ae957fe","tid":926692,"uid":184247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"未來大勢所趨，HKMA, HKSFC, SGMAS, etc. 黎緊幾年都係講Risk同Technology Topics，而且依行好封閉，有機會可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}